### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  AI-MSHM  –  Centers Endpoints
###  Base prefix: /api/v1/centers/
###
###  Roles involved:
###    patient        → no access here (read-only via their own dashboard)
###    clinician      → can create/read/update own ClinicianProfile
###    hcc_admin      → manages their HCC (admin panel)
###    fhc_admin      → manages their FHC (admin panel)
###    admin          → full CRUD on all centers
###
###  PUBLIC endpoints (no token needed):
###    GET /centers/hcc/   → list HCCs for dropdown in registration
###    GET /centers/fhc/   → list FHCs for dropdown in registration
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@baseUrl        = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@contentType    = application/json

# Tokens — fill in after login
@accessToken         = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@clinicianToken      = PASTE_CLINICIAN_TOKEN_HERE
@adminToken          = PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE


### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  PUBLIC — Center Dropdowns  (no auth needed)
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List all active Health Care Centers  (for registration dropdown)
GET {{baseUrl}}/centers/hcc/

### List all active Federal Health Centers  (for registration dropdown)
GET {{baseUrl}}/centers/fhc/


### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  CLINICIAN — Register  (new user flow)
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1. Register as clinician
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "full_name": "Dr. Amara Nwosu",
  "email": "dr.amara@clinic.com",
  "password": "Secure1234!",
  "confirm_password": "Secure1234!",
  "role": "clinician"
}

### 2. Verify email (paste token from email)
# POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-email/
# { "token": "PASTE_TOKEN" }

### 3. Login as clinician
# @name clinicianLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "clinician@demo.com",
  "password": "Demo1234!"
}


### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  CLINICIAN — Own Profile  (requires clinician role)
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### GET own clinician profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/centers/clinician/profile/
Authorization: Bearer {{clinicianToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### CREATE clinician profile  –  link to a Health Care Center (HCC)
###   First call GET /centers/hcc/ to find the hcc id
POST {{baseUrl}}/centers/clinician/profile/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{clinicianToken}}

{
  "specialization": "obstetrics_gynae",
  "license_number": "MDCN-2019-54321",
  "years_of_experience": 8,
  "bio": "Specialist in reproductive health and PCOS management.",
  "center_type": "hcc",
  "hcc": 1
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### CREATE clinician profile  –  link to a Federal Health Center (FHC)
POST {{baseUrl}}/centers/clinician/profile/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{clinicianToken}}

{
  "specialization": "internal_medicine",
  "license_number": "MDCN-2018-11111",
  "years_of_experience": 12,
  "bio": "Senior physician at federal level.",
  "center_type": "fhc",
  "fhc": 1
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### UPDATE clinician profile  (partial – send only changed fields)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/centers/clinician/profile/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{clinicianToken}}

{
  "bio": "Updated professional bio.",
  "years_of_experience": 9
}


### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  ADMIN — Health Care Center  (requires is_staff=True)
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List all HCCs (admin sees inactive too)
GET {{baseUrl}}/centers/admin/hcc/
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Create a new HCC
POST {{baseUrl}}/centers/admin/hcc/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Surulere General Hospital",
  "code": "SGH-001",
  "state": "Lagos",
  "lga": "Surulere",
  "address": "5 Western Avenue, Surulere, Lagos",
  "phone": "+2348011111111",
  "email": "admin@sgh.gov.ng",
  "status": "active",
  "notify_on_severe": true,
  "notify_on_very_severe": true
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Get HCC detail  (replace 1 with real id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/centers/admin/hcc/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Update HCC  (e.g. change notification settings)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/centers/admin/hcc/1/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "notify_on_severe": true,
  "notify_on_very_severe": true,
  "status": "active"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Deactivate HCC
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/centers/admin/hcc/1/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "inactive"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Delete HCC  ⚠️  Permanent
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/centers/admin/hcc/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  ADMIN — Federal Health Center
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List all FHCs
GET {{baseUrl}}/centers/admin/fhc/
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Create FHC
POST {{baseUrl}}/centers/admin/fhc/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Federal Medical Centre Kano",
  "code": "FMC-KAN-001",
  "state": "Kano",
  "zone": "North West",
  "address": "Hospital Road, Nassarawa, Kano",
  "phone": "+2348022222222",
  "email": "info@fmckano.gov.ng",
  "status": "active"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Get FHC detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/centers/admin/fhc/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Update FHC
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/centers/admin/fhc/1/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "active"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Delete FHC  ⚠️  Permanent
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/centers/admin/fhc/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


